description.p:
The invention offers the following advantages:
Requires fewer lead components for manufacturing a lead connector assembly;
Allows reliable mechanical inter-connection of connector elements of different materials;
Simplifies the assembly process;
Provides a rigid connector design; and
Same connector elements and similar manufacturing process can be used for both passive and active fixation lead connectors.

The invention together with further objects and advantages thereof, may best be understood by making reference to the following description taken together with the accompanying drawings, in which:
